Investment routines

Money aspect:

52 week lows & Top losers
-	Check at least 100 stocks that reach new lows.
-	Run through screener.
-	Done daily each morning

Special situations
-	Bankruptcy like ACY
-	Merger and acquisition
-	Spinoff

Low PBs.
Magic 6’s
-	PB < 0.6
-	PE < 6x
-	Dividend yield > 0.06
-	Done weekly

Net nets. (current assets – total liabilities > 0 )
-	Focus on Altman criteria, at least the balance sheet criteria like retained earnings > 0 (automatically satisfied ca > cl, but not sure about D/E)
-	Eliminate retained Earnings < 0
-	Eliminate  D > E

Business Aspect:

Upside risk and downside risk

Robustness to interest rate normalization

Supply and demand

Competition

Any moat

People Aspect
Quality of management
Insider ownership


